about.summary: Performs score test using saddlepoint approximation to estimate the null distribution. Also prepares summary statistics for meta-analysis and performs meta-analysis to combine multiple association results.

name: r-spatest
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '3.0.0' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-spatest
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/SPAtest_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/SPAtest/SPAtest_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 3ead98ce9aefc1f4f69dab70e2e0331de618f78bddabd7361d94f402e4aa085f

build:
  noarch: generic
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1001
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('SPAtest')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('SPAtest')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/leeshawn/SPAtest
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Performs score test using saddlepoint approximation to estimate the null distribution.
    Also prepares summary statistics for meta-analysis and performs meta-analysis to
    combine multiple association results.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - johanneskoester
    - bgruening
    - daler
    - jdblischak
    - cbrueffer
    - dbast
    - endrebak
